2013-08-25 v2.0.0
-----------------

* Upgrade to SS3 compatibility.
* Report settings fields are now generated in a `getSettingsFields` method,
  rather than using the `updateReportsSettingsFields` system.
* The field formatting system has changed from an using evals to using
  callbacks.

2013-08-04 v1.2.1
-----------------

* Fixed reference to LastModified that should be LastEdited

2013-07-31 v1.2.0
-----------------

* Added emailing of scheduled reports
* Included has_ones in the fields available for a generic data object report
  to assist in filtering


2011-11-28 v1.1.2
-----------------

* Dotted fields are escaped properly on pagination vars

2011-11-21 v1.1.1
-----------------

* Added ability to specify your own addition method for items being summed in 
  rows so to provide the ability to handle adding non-numeric types more 
  gracefully (eg times)

2011-11-18 v1.1.0
-----------------

* Added ability to specify parameters for conditions that get bound
  by either a GET value, or by specifying a default in the 
  ReportParams key value field

2011-08-25 v1.0.0
-----------------

* Added the ability to filter / bind condition values at the last minute for
  conditions. Simply provide a prefix and a callable in getConditionFilters;
  see AdvancedReport::getConditionFilters() for an example.
* Moved the settings of the report to a separate tab

2011-04-05 v0.1.2
-----------------

* Fixed problem where empty values were not being passed through to formatting functions
* Fixed formatting of table in PDF
* Allow PDF previews

2011-03-28 v0.1.1
-----------------

* Ability to specific IS NOT NULL and IS NULL conditions

2011-02-15 v0.1.0
-----------------

* First release
